Read `docs/BLUEBOOK.md` before planning or implementing product work.

Rules:
- Eazy Review is a mobile-first sneaker/product review and discovery app.
- Core flow is Browse -> Product Detail -> Eazy Score / Community Score -> My Rating.
- Use `Eazy Score`, `Community Score`, and `My Rating` in UI.
- Browsing must not require login.
- Rating must require login.
- Do not start with scraping, social features, comments, likes, push notifications, dark mode, admin dashboards, or advanced recommendations.
- Product direction in `docs/BLUEBOOK.md` outranks tool suggestions.
